  1.1 Background .......................................... 1
2. Methodology ............................................ 2
  2.1 Data Collection ..................................... 2
    2.1.1 Survey Design .................................. 2
3. Results ............................................... 3

Note that the TOC is automatically generated based on the sectioning commands used in the document, so you don't need to manually create a TOC or update it when you make changes to the document.

